==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Figurable
<hw>Fig`ur*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>figurare</ets> to form, shape, fr. <ets>figura</ets> figure: cf. F.
<ets>figurable</ets>. See <er>Figure</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being
brought to a fixed form or shape.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lead is <qex>figurable</qex>, but water is not.</q>
<rj><qau>Johnson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Figural</ent>⟦br⟧
